Kinnick Stadium

Inside the Kinnick Stadium Press Box, state-of-the-art amenities meet the tradition and ambiance of Kinnick Stadium, creating a first-class atmosphere for your wedding.  The University of Iowa's newly renovated facility offers four different event spaces to accommodate groups of every size.  

Located on the University of Iowa campus, just two miles off of Interstate 80, makes the Kinnick Stadium Press Box easily accessible from any direction.
